28b054df","tid":825541,"uid":29930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:36:23.000Z","msg":"點解食完牛雜d屎會黑色？"},{"pid":"4356f78deb175432d8889521593fe1bbab42b079","tid":825541,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:45:26.000Z","msg":"接受唔到牛肺同膀嘅質感<br />\n但鐘意食牛肚牛腸"},{"pid":"169c46e926c160d3e2eef910c72d4c446ea39071","tid":825541,"uid":58627,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:50:53.000Z","msg":"牛雜好應該一碗碗唔應該一串串<br />\n樓主係一個錯誤嘅示範<br />\n牛雜係一樣完整嘅美食，<br />\n不能夠以個人喜好去區分邊part好食<br />\n因為牛雜就係牛雜<br />\n佢每一部份都係有優勝之處<br />\n識食就一定食牛肚先<br />\n佢嘅煙韌感可以刺激你牙齒神經，<br />\n會有一定開胃作用<br />\n跟住就牛肺，<br />\n佢輕輕嘅爽口感就輕輕咁舒緩口部緊張，<br />\n加上牛肺具有嘅牛味，<br />\n慢慢將你導入牛雜嘅世界。<br />\n呢個時候即刻食舊蘿蔔過一過浸味，<br />\n保持口腔清爽。<br />\n爽快過後就到軟綿綿嘅牛膀，<br />\n呢個時候你會細味到牛腩汁嘅味道，<br />\n但你會發覺股味道係未夠！<br />\n牛腸就係完美帶出牛腩汁味道嘅部份。<br />\n殊吓殊吓，咬吓咬吓，<br />\n自然會真正領悟到整碗牛雜嘅精華。<br />\n<br />\n所以話，一碗碗嘅牛雜先係牛雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7219eab40c87285d5f905441e2658cc6bb385fdc","tid":825541,"uid":6715,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;膀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e49aea2e9113f62d56b62505d1e5938612f3b28","tid":825541,"uid":6715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"點解無聽過人話食牛肝？"},{"pid":"c9728f5a68c690d2ffd93c92eb71b510cbb750dd","tid":825541,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7219eab40c87285d5f905441e2658cc6bb385fdc","tid":825541,"uid":6715,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;膀<img src=\"/assets/f